      "date": "2013-06-05 15:14:31.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/2ee8bcfe-cdee-11e2-ba28-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
